latestPosts.caption:
Our most dreamy stay ever at Antaraa by @saffronstays @saffronstayswithyou located at Karjat, Maharashtra 💫🌿

📍Antaraa, Karjat is just 62 km away from Mumbai, Maharashtra!

🏡 Supremely aesthetic corners in every frame 🎨
🛏️ Cozy rooms with a view to die for 🌄
🏊‍♀️ Pool with mountain views? YES PLEASE 💙🏔️
🧺 Cutest picnic spot straight out of Pinterest 🌸🧃
🌅 Surreal sunrise & sunset that stole our hearts 🌞🌇
🎠 Adorable play area for the inner child 💫
👨‍🍳 Staff so warm, they felt like family 💕
🍲 Good food = Good mood 🍛😋
🔥 Barbecue night under a sky full of stars ✨🌌
🥄 Pahado vali panipuri – a burst of nostalgia 💚💦

Came for a workation, stayed for the vibes 💻☕
📸 Trust me, My view is better than your view! 😍🏞️
